nd"/>): „верхняя часть (тела животного)“. Более определенное родство с <ref type="xr" target="#entry_barc"/> ‘грива’,</etym><etym xml:lang="en">The word is related to the stem %ibarz%i- ‘high’ (see <ref type="xr" target="#entry_bærzond"/>): “upper part (of animal's body)”. A more definite relation is with the word <ref type="xr" target="#entry_barc"/> ‘mane’.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>